{"tid":1916491,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃田打手］牛旨商店 在家高汁一人火鍋feedback","createTime":"2020-03-09T01:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T14:03:48.000Z","uid":13361,"like":71,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9669c92938c2965bdd927dafc7f6cf429d640378","tid":1916491,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YNIq2JnLHPg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYNIq2JnLHPg&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=2a7a056a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YNIq2JnLHPg</a><br />\n我係排隊pop-up買新年套裝嘅傻仔<br />\n首先想講嘅係仆街仔馬田遲到咗半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無買到個爐 就咁買咗兩set料 分別係豬骨湯同醬油湯咁就一個美國肥牛一個荷蘭豬肉 我自己就咁煮熟佢食<br />\n<br />\n無論牛豬定湯底都屌打吉邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然係貴啲 但全部都日本料 重點係個芝士竹輪好好食 好食過吉邊個粒 <br />\n而且加料只要$20 就4粒 係超市平時買都要$4粒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> $300仲免運費 唔知點賺錢<br />\n今次我買兩set邊爐料再加5set芝士竹輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定食到佢蝕本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6jcyw6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6jcyw6.png&h=aa139c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink在此 <a href=\"https://www.meatnpot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meatnpot.com%2F&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=11f8942d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.meatnpot.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n（最近仲推出左番茄湯底）但我唔食番茄嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ee8dc024841db35d1d185a3c1155c7ec828e9","tid":1916491,"uid":177955,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"藍田<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405250e11b2ce9214294be21d4da4aa4b18f2fcf","tid":1916491,"uid":303628,"like":0,"dis